title: Inaudible Whispers in a Thunderstorm
description:
Welcome to episode 6 of Sleep and Relax ASMR! Today's episode features inaduible whispers in a rainstorm! Great for those who prefer abstract noises and whispers as opposed to storytelling.

Get in touch with the show: SleepandRelaxASMR@gmail.com 

Thanks to Mike Koenig (freesound.org) for some of the audio used this episode!
